msgctxt "7344"
msgid ""
"疲れたろ？\n"
"随分、長い散歩になった。"
msgstr "Are you tired? It was a long walk."

msgctxt "7381"
msgid ""
"ううん、全然平気。\n"
"寺田屋の仕事に比べたらこんなん……"
msgstr ""
"Yeah, I'm fine at all. Compared to the work of Teradaya, it's like this ..."

msgctxt "7436"
msgid ""
"一（はじめ）さんこそ、うちと２人きりで\n"
"疲れたんとちゃう？"
msgstr "Is Mr. Ichi (Hajime) tired of being alone with us?"

msgctxt "7495"
msgid "せやけどうちは……　とっても楽しかった。"
msgstr "But we ... It was a lot of fun."

msgctxt "7536"
msgid ""
"またこうして一（はじめ）さんと\n"
"町を歩けたらええなって……"
msgstr ""
"Also, if I could walk around the town with Ichi (Hajime) in this way ..."

msgctxt "7595"
msgid "……なあ、おりょう。"
msgstr "…… Hey, Oryo."

msgctxt "7617"
msgid "……ん？　何？"
msgstr "……Hmm? what?"

msgctxt "7632"
msgid ""
"今までありがとうな。\n"
"お前には感謝してる。"
msgstr "Thank you so far. I thank you."

msgctxt "7675"
msgid ""
"俺がこの町でなんとか１人でもやってこられたのは、\n"
"お前のおかげだ。"
msgstr "It's thanks to you that I managed to come by myself in this town."

msgctxt "7743"
msgid "なのに俺は、これまで礼のひとつも言わなかった。"
msgstr "But I haven't said one of the thanks so far."

msgctxt "7790"
msgid "今日になってやっと……"
msgstr "Only today ..."

msgctxt "7814"
msgid ""
"もう会えないかもしれない今になって、\n"
"やっと礼を言うなんてな。"
msgstr ""
"Now that I may not be able to meet you anymore, I can finally thank you."

msgctxt "7877"
msgid "一（はじめ）さん……"
msgstr "Mr. Ichi (beginning) ……"

msgctxt "7898"
msgid ""
"幕府がなくなって、世の中はこれから大きく変わる。\n"
"きっとよくなる。"
msgstr ""
"With the disappearance of the Shogunate, the world will change dramatically."
" I'm sure it will improve."

msgctxt "7965"
msgid ""
"だからおりょう。\n"
"お前は、女将さんたちといつまでも達者で……"
msgstr "That's why. You are a master with the landlady forever ..."

msgctxt "8027"
msgid "……そんなん嫌や。"
msgstr "...... I don't like that."

msgctxt "8046"
msgid "……ん？"
msgstr "……Hmm?"

msgctxt "8055"
msgid "その続きは、なんとなく想像つく。"
msgstr "I can imagine the continuation."

msgctxt "8088"
msgid ""
"せやけどうちは……\n"
"一（はじめ）さんの遺言なんて、聞きたない……"
msgstr "I haven't heard of Mr. Ichi (Hajime)'s will ..."

msgctxt "8153"
msgid "おりょう……"
msgstr "Oryo ……"

msgctxt "8166"
msgid ""
"一（はじめ）さんのこと騙してたうちが\n"
"言うことやないかもしれん。"
msgstr "I may not be able to say that I was deceiving Mr. Ichi (Hajime)."

msgctxt "8231"
msgid ""
"けど、うちはこれからも……\n"
"ずっと一（はじめ）さんのそばにいたい。"
msgstr ""
"However, we will continue to ... I want to be with Mr. Ichi (Hajime) "
"forever."

msgctxt "8298"
msgid ""
"なのに一（はじめ）さん、なんでもう二度と\n"
"会えへんような言い方するの？"
msgstr ""
"But Ichi (Hajime) -san, why do you say that you will never meet again?"

msgctxt "8369"
msgid "土佐で用事済ませたら、また京に戻ってくるんやろ？"
msgstr "After finishing the work in Tosa, will I come back to Kyoto again?"

msgctxt "8424"
msgid "お願いやから、必ず帰ってきて……"
msgstr "Please be sure to come back ..."

msgctxt "8457"
msgid ""
"うちは待ってるから。\n"
"一（はじめ）さんが戻ってくるまで、\n"
"ずっと待ってるから。"
msgstr "We are waiting. I'll be waiting for you until Ichi (Hajime) returns."

msgctxt "8536"
msgid ""
"約束して、一（はじめ）さん……\n"
"またこの町に戻ってくるって……"
msgstr "I promised, Mr. Ichi (Hajime) ... I'll be back in this town again ..."

msgctxt "8599"
msgid "分かった……　約束する。"
msgstr "Okay ... I promise."

msgctxt "8624"
msgid ""
"きっとやで。　嘘ついたら……\n"
"もう二度とご飯の支度してあげへんから。"
msgstr "I'm sure. If you lie ... I'll never prepare rice again."

msgctxt "8693"
msgid "……ああ。"
msgstr "……Oh."

msgctxt "10339"
msgid "龍馬"
msgstr "Ryoma"

msgctxt "10366"
msgid "おりょう"
msgstr "Oryo"
